06:33.287 --> 06:35.555
you have not come close enough.

06:42.167 --> 06:43.966
Turn over and lie still.

06:52.527 --> 06:55.726
Harriett, may I have
clean water in my jug?

07:01.047 --> 07:03.406
Why does nobody want her?

07:03.407 --> 07:05.166
Mr. Lynch said that she withdrew

07:05.167 --> 07:07.236
when he went to touch her.

07:07.261 --> 07:09.046
