07:09.047 --> 07:10.246
If he'd have taken her,

07:10.247 --> 07:11.606
it'd have paid off half our debts.

07:11.607 --> 07:14.286
Now Lennox wants his loan
and we can't pay it back.

07:14.287 --> 07:15.926
Three days, Will.

07:15.927 --> 07:17.486
Three days and the rent is due,

07:17.487 --> 07:19.046
and I haven't got it.

07:19.047 --> 07:20.926
Business will pick up.

07:20.927 --> 07:23.308
We've still got our regulars.

07:26.247 --> 07:28.440
I'm going to see Charlotte.

07:30.167 --> 07:31.846
You all right?

07:31.847 --> 07:33.046
