Death to destroy my trade!

08:02.847 --> 08:04.966
Rest, Mother, rest.

08:08.967 --> 08:10.286
It was a picture.

08:10.287 --> 08:11.486
Mrs. Wells cursing

08:11.487 --> 08:13.166
and Mrs. Scanwell crying "Demon!"

08:14.807 --> 08:17.486
How deliciously vulgar!

08:17.487 --> 08:20.726
I swear she'll flounder
before the week is out.

08:27.607 --> 08:31.686
The Spartans are preparing
for their sacred games.

08:31.687 --> 08:35.126
They would like a sacrifice
to augur their success.

08:35.126 --> 08:36.686
Oh, spit it out.

08:36.687 --> 08:38.566
You want to spoil another virgin.

08:38.567 --> 08:41.126
Allow me my metaphors.

08:41.126 --> 08:43.525
Do they make your
enterprise any less vile?

08:43.527 --> 08:45.646
The terms will be the same.

08:45.647 --> 08:47.166
No.

08:47.167 --> 08:48.766
Your Spartans all have names.

08:48.767 --> 08:50.566
I want one, that's my price.

08:50.567 --> 08:53.046
I have sworn an oath of secrecy.

08:53.047 --> 08:56.546
A pox on your oath, my neck is at stake!

08:57.047 --> 08:58.766
Knowledge is security.

08:58.767 --> 09:01.234
One girl, one name.

09:03.167 --> 09:06.006
This house and its vile harlots...

09:06.007 --> 09:07.646
