09:07.647 --> 09:09.926
Have you no culls with you, Mr. North?

09:09.927 --> 09:11.686
I've got no standing around here.

09:11.687 --> 09:13.648
Margaret Wells!

09:15.007 --> 09:17.806
Margaret Wells is an enemy of God!

09:17.807 --> 09:19.646
Does that woman never rest?

09:23.728 --> 09:25.406
Good mornin'.

09:30.167 --> 09:32.326
Why don't you knock on the door?

09:32.327 --> 09:34.326
