10:07.687 --> 10:09.446
Then you just nod and smile

10:09.447 --> 10:11.446
and move 'em on to the easy bit.

10:11.447 --> 10:13.206
So you find it easy?

10:13.207 --> 10:16.295
If it's giving you no
pleasure, manage things,

10:16.567 --> 10:18.526
to bring them on.

10:18.527 --> 10:20.409
You can be bold.

10:21.327 --> 10:23.447
By grasping the nettle?

10:23.767 --> 10:25.154
Yes.

10:25.527 --> 10:27.767
It's an easy beast to tame.

10:30.807 --> 10:32.127
Here.

10:37.327 --> 10:40.084
Make yourself its mistress.

10:44.807 --> 10:48.166
Take a firm hold and set the pace.

10:48.167 --> 10:49.809
Like on a horse.

10:49.834 --> 10:51.406
Start with a trot...

10:52.767 --> 10:55.166
and build to a gallop.

10:55.167 --> 10:58.286
And the more aroused they believe you,

10:58.287 --> 11:00.806
the sooner the cannon
will fire its balls.

11:04.167 --> 11:07.646
I could bestride the
world with such a serpent!

11:07.647 --> 11:09.015
Oh!

11:09.567 --> 11:12.046
There's no easier chimp to master

11:12.047 --> 11:16.126
than a man in a bed with
a stiff little pintle.

11:18.207 --> 11:20.006
Sir George.

11:20.007 --> 11:21.493
Howard!

11:22.527 --> 11:26.046
Satan built a palace in the fiery pit...

11:26.047 --> 11:29.526
The thing that sets us apart
is the warmth of our welcome.

11:29.527 --> 11:31.206
It's different here.

11:31.207 --> 11:32.646
The culls we need, they don't want

11:32.647 --> 11:34.806
common girls singing bawdy songs.

11:34.807 --> 11:37.166
They want a good time, we
know how to give it to 'em.

11:37.167 --> 11:40.166
... in foul and flagrant
defiance of God's law,

11:40.167 --> 11:43.526
like Satan's Palace is pandemonium!

11:43.527 --> 11:46.006
She says our house is Satan's Palace.

11:50.407 --> 11:52.717
Then why don't we show her...

11:52.742 --> 11:54.406
how we dance?

11:54.407 --> 11:56.884
Margaret Wells!

12:22.647 --> 12:24.126
Keep scrubbin'!

12:30.687 --> 12:32.406
Inside now!

12:38.127 --> 12:40.046
A masquerade.

12:40.047 --> 12:42.286
You should charge the highest price,

12:42.287 --> 12:43.526
and have a password,

12:43.527 --> 12:45.843
so only those who have it can get in.

12:46.407 --> 12:48.166
Pandemonium.

12:48.167 --> 12:49.446
I adore it.

12:50.647 --> 12:53.166
Oh, I'll invite some
sparkling cheap sorts,

12:53.167 --> 12:54.926
add some spice.

12:54.927 --> 12:57.406
I could even snag Lord Fallon.

12:57.407 --> 13:00.408
He's an icy fish but the
whole world follows him.

13:01.407 --> 13:03.646
She's done you a favor,

13:03.647 --> 13:05.126
that preacher.

13:05.127 --> 13:06.646
How?

13:06.647 --> 13:08.676
She's made you notorious.

13:09.527 --> 13:11.806
You're the bad bawd of London, Ma.

13:11.807 --> 13:14.871
When I've striven so hard to be so good.

13:15.287 --> 13:17.886
I'll do your pimping at
The Cocoa Tree tonight.

13:17.887 --> 13:19.818
Take Lucy with you.

13:20.018 --> 13:22.047
See if you can help her.

13:24.167 --> 13:25.806
As an instrument of the law,

13:25.807 --> 13:28.286
