13:28.287 --> 13:30.166
Yes, sir, absolutely.

13:30.167 --> 13:32.046
When a man knows your vice,

13:32.047 --> 13:33.926
he can use you, can't he?

13:33.927 --> 13:37.324
And in your position,
that's a dangerous thing.

13:37.927 --> 13:39.806
Yes, yes, sir.

13:39.807 --> 13:42.046
Take this to Quigley's in Golden Square

13:42.047 --> 13:44.006
