13:44.007 --> 13:47.286
That's a... brothel, sir.

13:49.007 --> 13:50.566
I like you, Oswald.

13:50.567 --> 13:52.046
You're efficient.

13:52.047 --> 13:53.406
I'd hate to lose you

13:53.407 --> 13:55.787
for the sake of your filthy fuck.

14:13.887 --> 14:15.495
What's this for?

14:15.927 --> 14:17.952
Your betterment.

14:18.287 --> 14:20.406
I can't see you anymore.

14:20.431 --> 14:21.806
I'm sorry.

14:24.407 --> 14:26.870
Margaret Wells' mother...

14:26.895 --> 14:31.167
