14:45.527 --> 14:46.926
Where is she?

14:46.927 --> 14:48.406
With my sister.

14:48.407 --> 14:50.406
... walking upon the earth.

15:04.527 --> 15:06.047
For you.

15:15.167 --> 15:17.686
You've stood by all this time

15:17.687 --> 15:20.006
