20:32.487 --> 20:34.286
Sir George, may I present Mr. D...

20:34.287 --> 20:35.486
Leave.

20:35.487 --> 20:36.766
I haven't finished playing.

20:36.767 --> 20:38.486
Well, I'm ordering
you back to the house.

20:38.487 --> 20:41.726
- You're making yourself foolish.
- No, you have done that.

20:43.487 --> 20:44.806
Go back to the house

20:44.807 --> 20:46.766
or I'll take you there myself.

21:02.647 --> 21:04.919
My sister's still inside.

21:05.407 --> 21:07.246
But you cannot go back in.

21:10.287 --> 21:12.286
I misplayed my hand.

21:12.287 --> 21:13.966
I let the mask slip for a moment

21:13.967 --> 21:16.425
and he saw me laugh at him.

21:19.967 --> 21:21.446
- Over here.
- Sir.

21:21.447 --> 21:23.326
I'll see your sister safely home.

21:25.567 --> 21:27.089
Thank you.

21:33.687 --> 21:35.446
But be wary.

21:35.447 --> 21:38.064
There are snares all
around for us harlots.

22:14.647 --> 22:16.206
Haxby!

22:22.007 --> 22:24.006
Where's your master?

22:24.007 --> 22:26.480
He has not yet come home.

22:26.927 --> 22:29.526
Perhaps he sought
more congenial company.

22:29.527 --> 22:31.246
Oh, dear.

22:31.247 --> 22:32.686
Spurned for another.

22:32.687 --> 22:34.676
How will I ease my poor heart?

22:35.207 --> 22:38.621
I didn't know you had
such an organ in your body.

22:39.527 --> 22:42.246
I swear you're missing
an organ, too, Haxby.

22:54.287 --> 22:56.046
Mother.

22:56.047 --> 22:57.686
Mrs. Quigley is here.

22:57.687 --> 22:59.486
- Mrs. Quigley?
- No, no, no,

22:59.487 --> 23:01.766
do not trouble yourself,
dear Mrs. Scanwell.

23:01.767 --> 23:04.246
Amelia tells me you are unwell.

23:04.247 --> 23:05.639
Here, child.

23:06.047 --> 23:09.086
Run to the apothecary
for a soothing draft.

23:21.927 --> 23:23.846
I trust you will be recovered enough

23:23.847 --> 23:25.650
to preach tonight.

23:26.927 --> 23:28.646
Margaret Wells' wickedness

23:28.647 --> 23:31.847
cannot be allowed to proceed unchecked.

23:32.247 --> 23:35.857
I will do your bidding
no longer, Mrs. Quigley.

23:36.527 --> 23:38.766
My daughter and I will
seek new accommodations

23:38.767 --> 23:40.447
as soon as I am able.

23:42.287 --> 23:45.322
I have a story I would share with you.

23:46.767 --> 23:50.302
The tale of a shameless whore,

23:50.327 --> 23:52.806
whom I once saw cavorting with her cull

23:52.807 --> 23:54.619
in plain sight.

23:55.287 --> 23:57.646
It was such a lascivious display

23:57.647 --> 24:00.619
from a young woman without fear...

24:00.644 --> 24:02.927
or decency.

24:03.351 --> 24:07.006
I've watched her progress
with interest ever since.

24:12.327 --> 24:15.046
What was your name in those days?

24:17.527 --> 24:19.686
Does your congregation know?

24:21.527 --> 24:23.246
Or your daughter?

24:27.327 --> 24:30.046
Enjoy your preaching, Mrs. Scanwell.

24:40.247 --> 24:42.246
- There you are.
- Thank you.

24:42.247 --> 24:43.446
Good day.

25:19.247 --> 25:20.526
Oh, no!

25:20.527 --> 25:21.692
No!

25:23.207 --> 25:24.926
After everything that I've done for you?

25:24.927 --> 25:26.686
Please, please, please,
Charlie, just let me go.

25:26.687 --> 25:28.646
How could you think of
running away from me?

25:28.647 --> 25:31.205
I can't stay here, it's torment!

25:31.487 --> 25:33.486
But I'm looking after you.

25:36.767 --> 25:38.808
It isn't right that she
treats me like a little boy.

25:38.833 --> 25:40.028
I'm a man.

25:40.447 --> 25:42.687
It's time she saw that.

25:52.007 --> 25:53.766
You saw me steal.

25:53.767 --> 25:55.447
Why didn't you call the watch?

25:56.908 --> 25:59.615
It was not for me to judge.

26:01.007 --> 26:03.110
Bloody purse was empty anyway.

26:04.567 --> 26:06.405
You got any money?

26:08.503 --> 26:10.263
Come on then.

26:20.687 --> 26:22.006
Take a flower?

26:22.007 --> 26:23.646
Fresh cut this morning.

26:30.007 --> 26:31.926
Penny for a posy, my lady?

26:31.927 --> 26:33.246
Hmm.

26:35.247 --> 26:38.440
Tell me, child, have you no family?

26:39.727 --> 26:41.006
Oh.

26:46.527 --> 26:49.373
I'll be trained to be a lady's maid?

26:49.847 --> 26:51.537
You will.

26:52.007 --> 26:53.206
The house is owned

26:53.207 --> 26:56.766
by a most charitable
Christian gentleman.

26:56.767 --> 27:00.382
We've placed half a dozen
girls in good households.

27:00.807 --> 27:03.246
I can hardly believe it.

27:03.247 --> 27:06.158
What did I do to deserve
such good fortune?

27:08.807 --> 27:11.585
Thank you, madam.

27:26.967 --> 27:29.766
Do I detect a small voice of conscience

27:29.767 --> 27:31.727
whispering in your ear?

27:36.487 --> 27:38.926
You going to try and save my soul?

27:41.767 --> 27:44.554
This is such a sinful world.

27:45.407 --> 27:48.134
Perhaps you're the one who needs saving.

27:48.567 --> 27:52.567
Vi, Nancy says we're to
meet her at Mrs. Wells'.

27:56.487 --> 27:57.806
You're leaving?

27:57.807 --> 28:00.381
The wages of sin don't earn themselves.

28:00.406 --> 28:02.325
Is she coming to Hades, too?

28:02.327 --> 28:05.006
Plenty of souls to save there.

28:05.007 --> 28:07.406
You want to see my world,
Scanwell's daughter?

28:26.247 --> 28:28.013
Have I tied it right?

28:28.038 --> 28:29.526
You're perfect, honey.

28:29.527 --> 28:31.166
We should earn some coin tonight.

28:31.167 --> 28:34.326
You do well, there'll be a place
here for you, Betsey Fletcher.

28:38.447 --> 28:40.286
Why don't I get a mask?

28:40.287 --> 28:42.006
Not you.

28:42.007 --> 28:44.086
It's different with you.

28:44.087 --> 28:45.743
You must be seen.

28:46.327 --> 28:47.846
You know that.

29:00.807 --> 29:03.511
Who is this handsome stranger?

29:03.536 --> 29:06.488
I feel strangely drawn to him.

29:06.847 --> 29:09.007
As you are to all handsome strangers.

29:14.647 --> 29:18.005
I'd pour gold into your lap
if I was sure of your love.

29:18.030 --> 29:20.316
You have it.

29:20.796 --> 29:22.327
I love you.

29:25.573 --> 29:28.053
I told you not to lie.

29:35.247 --> 29:38.086
So, you are the ferryman
who must be paid.

29:38.087 --> 29:39.766
No, Nancy.

29:39.767 --> 29:41.406
I am Hades,

29:41.407 --> 29:43.486
king of the underworld.

29:43.487 --> 29:45.046
And here's my queen.

29:46.767 --> 29:48.766
Tonight will be what we make it.

29:48.767 --> 29:51.246
Well, what you make it.

29:51.247 --> 29:54.006
'Cause you're Margaret
Wells, queen of bloody Soho.

30:11.487 --> 30:13.866
I was told there was a party.

30:14.647 --> 30:16.806
Take any girl you want.

30:16.807 --> 30:19.094
They're on the house!

30:19.119 --> 30:20.325
Take your pick.

30:20.327 --> 30:22.246
This way, you curs!

30:24.047 --> 30:25.766
Margaret Wells

30:25.767 --> 30:28.446
openly taunts God!

30:28.447 --> 30:33.046
Her house sits like a crusting scab

30:33.047 --> 30:35.686
over the suppurating boil of Hell.

30:35.687 --> 30:37.806
Thank you, Mrs. Scanwell.

30:37.807 --> 30:40.514
Thank you for showing
those sinners where to come.

30:41.767 --> 30:43.526
Welcome!

30:43.527 --> 30:45.938
Welcome, one and all.

30:45.963 --> 30:48.005
Welcome to my fiery hole.

30:50.007 --> 30:52.246
- Sinners all.
- Pandemonium.

30:52.247 --> 30:55.041
You test God's patience tonight.

30:55.066 --> 30:58.365
Hush, you'll be like
thoroughbreds amongst donkeys.

30:59.327 --> 31:00.486
Hurry.

31:00.487 --> 31:02.006
Where are you going?

31:02.007 --> 31:04.046
To the masquerade at Margaret Wells'.

31:04.047 --> 31:06.246
I shall take our girls
and steal her trade.

31:06.247 --> 31:08.486
That'll show Mother that
my judgment can be trusted.

31:08.487 --> 31:10.750
- Oh, take me with you.
- No.

31:11.287 --> 31:13.480
She's taken my allowance, Emily.

31:14.247 --> 31:16.593
You are a donkey.

31:17.687 --> 31:19.006
Marie-Louise, take a message

31:19.007 --> 31:20.646
to Mrs. Wells for me, I beg you.

31:20.647 --> 31:21.926
Tell her I want to come back,

31:21.927 --> 31:23.312
and tell her I'll do anything.

31:23.353 --> 31:24.508
_

31:24.533 --> 31:26.779
La Quigley, she will kill me.

31:31.087 --> 31:33.766
And there will be no respite

31:33.767 --> 31:36.046
and no succor...

31:36.047 --> 31:38.399
Are you moved to repent, sister?

31:38.424 --> 31:41.183
I'm not your sister, Ratface.

31:41.208 --> 31:43.246
Who are you to insult me?

31:43.247 --> 31:45.566
I earn my coins the same way as you.

31:45.567 --> 31:47.566
I don't earn mine spying for Dame Death.

31:47.567 --> 31:49.560
I do what I must to survive.

31:50.487 --> 31:52.291
Then do this.

31:53.007 --> 31:55.246
... to a foul reek.

31:55.247 --> 31:58.813
When the harlot in your
arms removes her mask,

31:59.807 --> 32:02.806
a grinning death's head
is all that you will see.

32:02.807 --> 32:04.246
Madam.

32:04.247 --> 32:07.128
I am the curate from St. Clement Danes.

32:07.153 --> 32:09.245
Hearing of your indisposition,

32:09.247 --> 32:12.246
I've come to preach in your stead.

32:12.247 --> 32:13.753
Who sent you?

32:14.207 --> 32:15.686
A friend.

32:18.847 --> 32:22.948
Mother, we must pray for
the kindness of that friend.

32:22.973 --> 32:24.332
Come.

32:29.365 --> 32:31.486
And the skulls will have eyes

32:31.487 --> 32:33.859
and the eyes will have jewels.

32:33.884 --> 32:36.765
And there will be feasting in hell

32:36.767 --> 32:39.286
with roasted swans and pigs' heads

32:39.287 --> 32:42.166
with apples dipped in virgin's blood,

32:42.167 --> 32:45.766
and sinners will lick nectar
from each other's stomachs,

32:45.767 --> 32:48.926
and those of firm and manly impulse...

32:48.927 --> 32:50.206
Welcome.

32:53.007 --> 32:54.766
Welcome.

32:57.767 --> 32:59.486
That's Lord Fallon.

32:59.487 --> 33:00.926
Told you I'd get him.

33:00.927 --> 33:02.781
I never doubted.

33:03.407 --> 33:05.766
Welcome to my midnight realm.

33:09.727 --> 33:11.486
Our visit won't be long.

33:11.487 --> 33:13.006
Pandemonium!

33:16.167 --> 33:18.046
Let the folderols begin!

33:24.847 --> 33:26.726
I'm here to work.

33:26.727 --> 33:29.006
Gentlemen, may I present

33:29.007 --> 33:31.526
a new and exotic addition to our house.

33:31.527 --> 33:33.246
Well, I never!

33:33.247 --> 33:36.486
By George, a black Venus.

33:36.487 --> 33:39.926
I am Dido, Queen of Carthage,

33:39.927 --> 33:43.222
fated to the underworld
for daring to love.

33:43.807 --> 33:45.286
Who dares love me?

33:45.287 --> 33:47.582
- Oh!
- Very nice.

33:48.047 --> 33:50.726
Now that's how a whore
makes an entrance.

33:50.727 --> 33:52.846
- Welcome, sir.
- Ladies.

34:07.386 --> 34:09.246
Look at you!

34:09.246 --> 34:10.766
I know!

34:48.596 --> 34:51.463
You promised me a
glimpse without your mask.

34:51.806 --> 34:53.525
You're too much, sir.

34:55.527 --> 34:56.886
Not now.

35:00.647 --> 35:02.888
You could almost be one of us.

35:08.287 --> 35:10.086
Your jealousy is absurd.

35:10.087 --> 35:12.286
He came with the Reptons,
I hardly know him.

35:12.287 --> 35:15.046
You think I don't know what
a faithless whore you are?

35:15.047 --> 35:16.166
You're right.

35:16.167 --> 35:17.806
I've pleasured every one of your friends

35:17.807 --> 35:19.206
behind your back,

35:19.207 --> 35:22.246
and we laugh at what a
credulous ass you are.

35:36.607 --> 35:40.420
♪ A master of musick ♪

35:40.445 --> 35:44.206
♪ Came with an intent ♪

35:44.207 --> 35:47.998
♪ To give me a lesson ♪

35:48.023 --> 35:51.926
♪ On my instrument ♪

35:51.927 --> 35:55.398
♪ I thank'd him for nothing ♪

35:55.423 --> 35:59.646
♪ And bid him be gone ♪

35:59.647 --> 36:03.426
♪ For my little fiddle ♪

36:03.451 --> 36:06.366
♪ Should not be played on ♪

36:07.607 --> 36:10.770
♪ My thing is my own ♪

36:10.795 --> 36:15.046
♪ And I keep it so still ♪

36:15.047 --> 36:18.760
♪ Though other young lasses ♪

36:18.785 --> 36:21.686
♪ May do as they will ♪

36:21.687 --> 36:22.886
Too right, we do!

36:22.887 --> 36:26.204
♪ My thing is my own ♪

36:26.229 --> 36:30.366
♪ And I keep it so still ♪

36:30.367 --> 36:34.153
♪ Though other young lasses ♪

36:34.178 --> 36:37.726
♪ May do as they will ♪

36:43.287 --> 36:44.886
Well done!

36:48.887 --> 36:50.686
You're like Persephone,

36:50.687 --> 36:52.420
aren't you?

36:52.445 --> 36:54.084
I don't know, sir.

36:55.327 --> 36:57.206
She was tricked into the underworld

36:57.207 --> 36:58.766
by eating pomegranate seeds.

36:58.767 --> 37:01.046
Come, Fallon, the games await.

37:04.469 --> 37:07.126
I'll take you to my underworld...

37:07.127 --> 37:08.686
one day.

37:12.327 --> 37:14.606
And a choir of heavenly bishops

37:14.607 --> 37:17.046
with buttocks opalescent as the moon

37:17.047 --> 37:19.126
will descend on the House of Wells...

37:19.127 --> 37:20.646
Go and seek the best culls

37:20.647 --> 37:23.145
and bring them away as fast as possible.

37:23.527 --> 37:25.326
- Lord Fallon.
- Mr. Osborne.

37:25.327 --> 37:26.566
No wonder you're leaving.

37:26.567 --> 37:28.145
Here is much finer sport.

37:29.287 --> 37:31.491
Go and finger your mother, Quigley.

37:33.087 --> 37:35.529
Donations, please.

37:37.407 --> 37:38.686
Thank you.

37:48.321 --> 37:50.846
That gets them in, not you.

37:50.847 --> 37:53.566
Twice as much again if
you want to gain entry.

38:09.527 --> 38:11.246
Sit down and shut up.

38:11.247 --> 38:12.766
I got money to make.

38:30.647 --> 38:34.966
There's a story about a feast in hell,

38:34.967 --> 38:36.766
where the forks are so long

38:36.767 --> 38:39.926
that people can't reach their mouths,

38:39.927 --> 38:42.801
so all the diners starve to death.

38:43.207 --> 38:46.206
They don't figure out that
they can feed each other.

38:57.887 --> 38:59.744
Sir.

39:05.607 --> 39:08.406
Pleasure, treasure, and carnage.

39:08.407 --> 39:10.846
I've always wanted to fuck royalty.

39:12.847 --> 39:16.926
Your dusky queen is
too delicious to resist.

39:19.127 --> 39:20.806
Four guineas for royalty.

39:52.647 --> 39:55.846
I was determined to be the first...

39:55.847 --> 39:57.722
to have you.

39:58.367 --> 40:00.526
You're a powerful man.

40:00.527 --> 40:02.943
I bet you always get what you want.

40:02.968 --> 40:04.726
Oh, I do.

40:08.367 --> 40:10.488
But tonight,

40:11.127 --> 40:12.755
I'm your queen,

40:13.167 --> 40:15.349
and you're my subject.

40:16.054 --> 40:18.002
And you're going to do...

40:18.727 --> 40:20.206
what I want.

40:28.767 --> 40:30.606
You're no queen.

40:32.847 --> 40:35.166
You're a goddess.

40:39.527 --> 40:41.286
I don't want no quarrel with her.

40:41.287 --> 40:44.366
I'll smile and smile
and bring you new custom.

40:44.367 --> 40:47.046
Mrs. Quigley does not
appreciate my talents.

40:55.607 --> 40:57.166
How much do you owe?

40:57.167 --> 40:59.526
Sixty, but I'll earn you three

40:59.527 --> 41:02.073
every time a penis comes my way.

41:03.257 --> 41:05.433
Sounds like a fair exchange.

41:07.327 --> 41:09.206
Quarrel be damned.

41:09.207 --> 41:11.079
I'll hide you upstairs.

41:11.407 --> 41:12.806
Go on.

41:23.247 --> 41:26.931
Well, I always knew you were a whore.

41:27.407 --> 41:29.206
For the first time in my life,

41:29.207 --> 41:30.686
I am paid.

41:44.527 --> 41:47.406
Well, aren't you full of surprises?

41:47.407 --> 41:48.766
Your lordship.

41:48.767 --> 41:51.726
There's a debt to pleasure
you still haven't paid,

41:51.727 --> 41:54.206
and we must remedy
that, don't you think?

41:54.207 --> 41:55.966
I have to speak to my mother.

41:55.967 --> 41:57.985
So she can charge me again?

41:59.207 --> 42:01.206
It's time to make good,

42:01.207 --> 42:02.766
loyal Lucy.

42:15.527 --> 42:17.166
There you are.

42:29.167 --> 42:31.086
Trying to keep out of trouble.

42:33.607 --> 42:34.966
Don't.

42:48.847 --> 42:51.258
Charlotte, you harlot.

42:52.087 --> 42:53.886
Keep your hands off my pirate.

42:53.887 --> 42:56.110
He's yours for the taking.

42:57.527 --> 42:59.966
Why are you hiding down here?

43:01.767 --> 43:05.246
Don't you want to sail on the high seas?

43:05.247 --> 43:07.183
Of course I do.

43:07.967 --> 43:10.246
My desire is an ocean.

43:10.247 --> 43:12.326
Spill it into me, you brute creature,

43:12.327 --> 43:13.766
you corsair.

43:13.767 --> 43:16.547
Now, on this table.

43:25.127 --> 43:26.766
Get off her, you're disgusting!

43:26.767 --> 43:29.200
Your sister doesn't
seem to think so, do you?

43:29.807 --> 43:31.446
- Do you?
- No.

43:31.447 --> 43:32.766
Maybe now you'll think twice

43:32.767 --> 43:35.246
before you lick honey
from that Irish rake.

43:36.927 --> 43:38.406
Just go.

43:49.207 --> 43:52.286
You gave Margaret Wells my girl?

43:52.287 --> 43:54.366
They spirited her away,
I couldn't find her.

43:54.367 --> 43:55.886
You went to that bitch's kennel

43:55.887 --> 43:57.406
with three pieces of my property.

43:57.407 --> 43:59.046
What did you think would happen?

43:59.047 --> 44:00.606
We meant to steal her trade.

44:00.607 --> 44:02.126
Yes, and instead, she stole mine.

44:02.127 --> 44:04.046
You let that she-hound
run rings around you,

44:04.047 --> 44:06.246
just like that sly harpy upstairs.

44:06.247 --> 44:07.606
Oh, you're a man, all right.

44:07.607 --> 44:09.086
Your brain always in your breeches,

44:09.087 --> 44:10.326
too swollen to think.

44:10.327 --> 44:11.762
That's hardly fair.

44:13.087 --> 44:14.854
I should've had a girl.

44:15.247 --> 44:17.046
No daughter of mine
would've allowed herself

44:17.047 --> 44:18.766
to be duped by a whore.

44:18.767 --> 44:21.268
Why were you the one I chose to keep?

44:36.767 --> 44:38.447
Move aside.

44:42.687 --> 44:44.967
I am not yours to command!

